      "title":"Old man inquires",
      "data":"old_man.png",
      "text":"Well, the cops want us to be silent with all this abuse taking place. I have not seen this kind of violence since Paquito's era. You should be able do dash over those spikes by pressing F while jumping. Try it out as I am too old for that... (Also, did you know Sleepy Joe won the election, what a time to be alive...)",
